User Stories:

User Story 1
As a horror game player 
I want to touch objects that has a percentage chance to jumpscare by interacting with the object/touching the object 
So that I can feel the adrenaline of jumpsacre

User Story 2
As a big fan of Halloween
I want to experience the scare and adrenalin of this game,
so that I can have a feel of this holiday the whole year.

Acceptance Criteria:

A jumpscare when the user touches an object in the room. 
A chance to add jumpscares in objects.
Jumpscare images can be halloween related (blood, clowns, etc.) last 5 - 10 seconds
Display Menu before playing 
